==Chinese==
===[[Mandarin]]===
[[Pinyin]]: héyì 

===Verb===
'''[[合]][[意]]'''

# to be pleased (with); to suit; to be to one's liking
#: ''[[如何]][[買]][[到]]'''合意'''[[二手]][[車]]'' ([[Traditional Chinese]])
#: ''[[如何]][[买]][[到]]'''合意'''[[二手]][[车]]'' ([[Simplified Chinese]])
#: ''How to buy a used-car that you will '''be pleased with'''.

